=begin pod
=head1 Bitfields

=head2 GtkStyleContextPrintFlags

Flags that modify the behavior of C<.to-string()>.

New values may be added to this enumeration.

=item C<GTK_STYLE_CONTEXT_PRINT_NONE>; Default value.
=item C<GTK_STYLE_CONTEXT_PRINT_RECURSE>; Print the entire tree of
  CSS nodes starting at the style context's node
=item C<GTK_STYLE_CONTEXT_PRINT_SHOW_STYLE>; Show the values of the
  CSS properties for each node
=item C<GTK_STYLE_CONTEXT_PRINT_SHOW_CHANGE>; Show information about
  what changes affect the styles
=end pod

